<l>pullavaiyuṭ poccāntuñ collaṟka nallavaiyu</l>
<l>ṇaṉku celaccollu vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are able to speak good things impressively in an assembly of the good should not even forgetfully speak them in that of the low</l>
